attr.title: Humming Out
attr.desc: A casual 2D pixel-art platformer with puzzle elements. You play as a small, fragile hummingbird navigating dark crystal caves filled with hostile creatures. Avoid obstacles and solve puzzles to escape the mysterious depths.
attr.inst:
You can purchase Humming Out at: https://mfproject.itch.io/hummin-out 

Download the Linux version and extract it, and place the HumminOut.x86_64.pck file in the gamedata directory. This has been tested with the HumminOut_Linux.zip, Dec 04 2022 release.
